- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses a routing technique in Wireless Sensor Networks.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper proposes a new technique to overcome coverage and energy holes, which involves organizing the nodes into clusters.
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a possibility as the paper may involve coordination between the nodes in the clusters.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper may involve optimizing the number of Cluster Heads using a learning algorithm.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper may involve controlling the behavior of the nodes in the network.
